code: public void testUserToString() {     User user = new User("u1", "r1").     assertThat(user.toString(), is("User[username=u1,roles=[r1],fullName=null,email=null,metadata={}]")).     user = new User("u1", new String[] { "r1", "r2" }, "user1", "user1@domain.com", Collections.singletonMap("key", "val"), true).     assertThat(user.toString(), is("User[username=u1,roles=[r1,r2],fullName=user1,email=user1@domain.com,metadata={key=val}]")).     user = new User("u1", new String[] { "r1" }, new User("u2", "r2", "r3")).     assertThat(user.toString(), is("User[username=u1,roles=[r1],fullName=null,email=null,metadata={}," + "authenticatedUser=[User[username=u2,roles=[r2,r3],fullName=null,email=null,metadata={}]]]")). }
